// Audit log for magic-link guest access to /api/intake-edit/*. These users
// don't have a `User` row (LINE-only identity), so they don't fit the
// AuditLog model which requires a userId FK. Separate table keeps the
// schema honest and lets us purge old rows on a different schedule.
